title: $4.5 Trillion Asset Manager Suggests Ethereum ($ETH) is Undervalued at Current Levels
description: The cryptocurrency-focused arm of the renowned investment titan Fidelity Investments, which has over $4.5 trillion in assets under management, has recently suggested the second-largest digital asset by market capitalization Ethereum ($ETH) is trading at a discount.
